column2: "Hello there. Sorry for sighing, I'm just a little tired."
"It seems like I'm fighting native creatures and not Darkers recently."
"I know they're partly our enemy, but I still can't get used to it."
"I don't think anyone who does get used to that can call themselves ARKS."
"I'm tired of fighting them, but I can't forget why I'm fighting."
"Thanks for listening. I'm going to get going now."
